step3:In first VM is using the installing docker ,and goto the /opt directory create one directory with the name of "nexus-data"
By using these command:mkdir -p /opt/nexus-data
Giving the file permissions :chmod -R 777 /opt/nexus-data

Step 4:And come back to the /root to create one nexus image

        docker pull sonatype/nexus3

Step 5:create one nexus continer with the port number 8081
        docker run -d \
  --name nexus \
  -p 8081:8081 \
  -v /opt/nexus-data:/nexus-data \
  --restart always \
  sonatype/nexus3

